EXPLAIN IN ANSWER:-
â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”
ğŸ‘‰ Data validation are checking the user inputs to make sure the entered data must be in the correct or complete in the expected format, before submitting a form.
ğŸ”¹ I use required field checks (IsBlank) to make sure important fields are not empty.
ğŸ”¹ I apply pattern validations using functions like IsMatch() â€” for example, validating email or phone number formats.
ğŸ”¹ I also use conditional visibility â€” like changing border colors or showing warnings based on input.

Example:
ğŸ‘‰ In one app, I built a registration form where I validated email format, mandatory fields, and showed custom error messages to guide users before submission.
